title: How I Upset EVERYONE In Warzone - Delivery Service Gone Wrong
author: PipBoy Fresh
description:
I spent a few hours trying to deliver up some hot and delicious snipes and kills in Warzone while I was disguised in a car. I got my Kar and Fennec out and drove all around Verdansk to use my Heartbeat GPS to find the right bounty target and dish out some of my goods. My customers may have not been in happy in my contracts and got me in the face, but all in all it was a great way to display the stopping power of a man in uniform. 

Like. Subscribe. Follow. Get a hold of me to stop, collaborate, and listen. 
Join us every Wednesday and Friday at 8:00 CST. Link in bio!
